node.text:
This property designed & built by @RaminDesigns . This Miami Beach mansion which broke the record of the highest price ($3,000) per square foot in Miami Beach. Located in the exclusive Venetian Islands, this stunning waterfront home embodies the ideal combination of modern Miami Beach design, unobstructed views, outstanding outdoors for waterfront living, and deluxe amenities put together in a tasteful yet indulgent fashion. With 12 foot high ceilings, 6600 sq ft of luxury living space this home offers 6 bedrooms and 6.5 bathrooms.

node.text:
This mega-mansion is soon to hit the market with a price tag only the super rich can afford: $500 million. When it goes on sale, it will become the most expensive house in the United States, eclipsing the Chartwell estate, known as the setting of "The Beverly Hillbillies" 
______

Dubbed "The One," the 100,000-square-foot #estate, located in Los Angeles' Bel-Air neighborhood, was designed by #luxury real estate developer @nileniami , who set out to build the most extravagant home in the U.S. Architecture by @mccleandesign 
______

Construction on the house began in 2013 and is expected to finish next year. Once completed, "The One" will also go above and beyond the classic amenities of a mega-mansion. Residents can curl up with a book in the glass-encased library or perfect their bowling game at the home's private four-lane alley.

Netflix binges will be taken to the next level in the 40-seat movie theater.

The house even hosts its own nightlife with an indoor/outdoor nightclub on the premises.

One of the estate's most distinguishing features will be the jellyfish room, where tanks of jellyfish replace the walls, illuminated by black lights.

Outside, four infinity pools will cover the grounds and a moat will circle the entire property. "It will feel like the house is floating on water," Niami says.

When the mansion is completed, he's confident the right buyer will scoop it up. "There's a lot of people out there with a lot of money they want something no one else can have," Niami says that this is it!
Via @luxury_listings

node.text:
Take a look inside this custom contemporary residence by @ramtin_ray_nosrati comprised of an array of creative features Including a 2 story car garage with a lift, bowling alley, game room, indoor and outdoor pool, cannabis lounge, theatre room, and waterfall entrance surrounded by fire. This house is truly remarkable and a statement of luxury.

node.text:
Offered at €17,500,000 
by @sothebysrealty 

Palatial, newly built, uniquely luxurious, state of the art villa with 1100 m² living space and extensive landscaped grounds. It has a 100m frontage onto the Vinkeveense lake (Plassen) and a 40m long private sandy beach. The villa has been developed with close attention to the smallest details. ⁣⁣⁣
Bedrooms:⁣ ⁣7⁣
Build: 1100 m²⁣
Lot: ⁣2 acres⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Very private and serene location where between high evergreen hedges, two double electric doors (in&out) connect the quiet road with the wide driveway. The +100m Vinkeveense Plassen water frontage has 3 integrated jetty terraces directly over the water. There are extensive mooring facilities.Continuing along the lake from the over water terraces and boat mooring frontage is a private 40 meters long white sandy beach. The Beach house has showers, bathrooms a BBQ and a bar with cooking facilities. | #housexterior #modernhome #luxuryhomes
